reviews.text: Decent if you are hungry. Service is good.

Went there for a late lunch (1:45pm). The place was only half full, but yet the waitress were busy chatting and ignored me. I finally had to get up from my table to go to the cashier to place my order. 

Prices are inexpensive, but quality-wise : average. 

Go with zero expectations, that way - you won't be disappointed. 😉
Lovely hong Kong Lai chai! And nice friendly staff 😊
Average fare. No complaints. Good bike (and motor bike) parking outside the cafe !

Average food with expensive price. Ordinary service. Bicycle racks is provided for cyclists who come here to eat. 
Suspect of running an illegal car park.
